data.description: Dacula's newest listing is here! This well-maintained 5 bedroom, 3 full bath home has all the space you and your family need with its 3100+ sqft layout. It's situated off of Harbins Rd. In the Harbin Landing Estates Subdivision.. just south of GA-316 in one of the best neighborhoods in the popular Harbins/McConnell/Archer school district. Situated on one of the largest lots available in the community, this home has a fully-fenced back yard, separate workshop and newly added gazebo for entertaining guest or just a quiet night in your spacious backyard. Once you step inside you'll find an open concept floorplan with formal dining room, keeping room/office,guest bedroom and full bath. A large kitchen with stainless steel appliance an island, granite counter tops, and lots of cabinet spaces. Off from the kitchen you look over into your family room with lots of sunlight. Upstairs are four additional bedrooms-including the spacious master with double vanity, seperate shower, soak in tub, and large walk in closet....This home also offers a  a bonus media room that's great for kids or a 2nd living room, and a dedicated laundry room on the upper level. What more can you ask for in a home?!?!?! Book your showing  today!
